    "http://ogp.me/ns#title": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "Danielle Allard  | Jukebox Lunch Concerts |  Thu, Jun 18, 2026, 12:10 pm | Peter A. Herrndorf Place"
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns#image": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "https://naccnaca-eventimages.s3.amazonaws.com/41077/danielleYallard__large.jpg"
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns#description": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "Singer-songwriter. Chameleon. Her tender voice and her combination of jazz, folk, pop, and blues will leave you pleasantly astounded. Danielle Allard is a singer-songwriter, multi-instrumentalist and music streamer. She has been performing publicly for over 15 years and graced stages across Canada and Europe. \n\nRecipient of the Capital Music Award for Solo Artist of the Year in 2023, Danielle has toured Germany, Portugal, Brazil and much of Canada, but also performs three times a week for an international audience as a music streamer. \n\nJukebox Lunch Concerts  \n\nEvery break deserves a..."
      }
    ],
